1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,539
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:38,020
Episode 19

3
00:01:38,509 --> 00:01:39,910
Put Kun opera

4
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:41,840
aside.

5
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,170
Next month, it’s the selection

6
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,330
of Opera Association.

7
00:01:45,509 --> 00:01:46,860
Don’t you want

8
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:49,000
to revenge for your dad?

9
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,340
If you perform Kun opera,

10
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:54,210
we may sustain losses in business.

11
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,090
Also, you may ruin your reputation,

12
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,910
which will influence your selection.

13
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:02,490
Do you want to wait 5 years more?

14
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,190
Please listen to me.

15
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:17,620
I’ll write a new play for you.

16
00:02:25,110 --> 00:02:25,730
OK.

17
00:02:27,850 --> 00:02:28,930
Please hurry.

18
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:32,050
I want to play that when the theater is open.

19
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,100
The theater is still in air.

20
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:36,480
You are thinking about its opening.

21
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:38,130
You!

22
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:40,250
Don’t urge me to write the play.

23
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,770
Urge Cheng Fengtai

24
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,440
to find a palace. Hurry.

25
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,600
What palace?

26
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:55,530
You always have many guests.

27
00:02:56,690 --> 00:02:57,140
OK.

28
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,230
I’ll go.

29
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:03,670
Mr. Cheng.

30
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:09,520
Mr. Cheng. Have a seat.

31
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,900
Look. Mr. An gave me some good tea.

32
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:12,590
Have a taste.

33
00:03:16,329 --> 00:03:19,060
I want you to perform an opera with me.

34
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,500
Can you perform opera?

35
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:22,360
What opera?

36
00:03:23,890 --> 00:03:26,280
A good one. Very interesting.

37
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,800
You will like it.

38
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,520
What’s the weird flavor?

39
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:17,750
Who is it?

40
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,260
You asked me

41
00:04:19,269 --> 00:04:21,350
to come.

42
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,780
How come you forget now?

43
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,870
Which one of you

44
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:29,040
asked a harlot here?

45
00:04:29,290 --> 00:04:30,160
We didn’t.

46
00:04:30,170 --> 00:04:31,040
No.

47
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,290
Did you?

48
00:04:32,450 --> 00:04:33,430
No.

49
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,030
No.

50
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:38,030
Go out and have a look.

51
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:57,970
Second chief.

52
00:04:58,140 --> 00:04:59,190
She’s a harlot.

53
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,740
And she looks sultry.

54
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:03,030
Will you open the door?

55
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,490
I’ll go if you don’t.

56
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,640
I won’t give your money back.

57
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,230
A harlot

58
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,290
came to us.

59
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,690
Why don’t we let her in

60
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:20,830
make us happy.

61
00:05:21,290 --> 00:05:21,760
Go.

62
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,810
Who are you?

63
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:36,230
I?

64
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:40,330
I am your Jinx.

65
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,770
-Witch.
-Witch.

66
00:05:53,980 --> 00:06:04,810
(Zhilan Middle School)

67
00:06:04,810 --> 00:06:05,330
My lady!
(Zhilan Middle School)

68
00:06:05,330 --> 00:06:08,840
(Zhilan Middle School)

69
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,660
Where is my brother?
(Zhilan Middle School)

70
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:10,970
He had something

71
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,040
and asked me to send you home.

72
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,450
I’ll go. See you.

73
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:15,580
Mr. Zheng,

74
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:17,800
I can drive you home.

75
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:21,400
I’m afraid this will bother you.

76
00:06:23,010 --> 00:06:24,080
My lady, what do you think?

77
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:28,030
Let’s go together.

78
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:29,670
Thanks.

79
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:32,990
Are you tired?

80
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,640
No.

81
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:35,290
Our classmates are good.

82
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,409
Well,

83
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:57,050
why are you fixing your eyes outside?

84
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,100
It’s late.

85
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:02,570
Why isn’t Laihong back?

86
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:04,830
It’s because you spoil him.

87
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,930
He doesn’t work hard on study

88
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,820
or come back

89
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,570
at dinner time.

90
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,730
Kids at this age,

91
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:17,040
especially boys,

92
00:07:17,050 --> 00:07:18,590
are all naughty.

93
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,120
OK. OK.

94
00:07:21,090 --> 00:07:21,650
Master,

95
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:23,790
Cheng Fengtai is here.

96
00:07:24,770 --> 00:07:25,830
Cheng Fengtai?

97
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,850
Mr. and Mrs. Zheng.

98
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,360
Good evening.

99
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:40,470
What brings

100
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,150
Mr. Cheng by?

101
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:45,860
You invited me to watch opera,

102
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:48,170
Followers Pavilion played by Shang Xirui.

103
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:52,390
Everything is perfect of that opera.

104
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:53,860
Today

105
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,610
I come to

106
00:07:56,110 --> 00:07:57,930
give you a show back.

107
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:02,590
Look at your man.

108
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,380
Li Jun

109
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,640
or Huang Tianba?

110
00:08:07,650 --> 00:08:09,470
Which opera you’ll play?

111
00:08:12,220 --> 00:08:13,300
Returning to Zhao.

112
00:08:17,370 --> 00:08:19,460
Chacha’er. Your English is good.

113
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,210
My brother taught me.

114
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,650
Mr. Cheng?

115
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,390
What?

116
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:30,920
I didn’t think

117
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,960
he allows me to make friends with you.

118
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:36,480
Our classmates told me

119
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,510
I’ll be executed if I make friends with you.

120
00:08:39,210 --> 00:08:40,580
Don’t believe their nonsense.

121
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,190
My brother is open-minded

122
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:43,760
and gentle.

123
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,580
He’s not scary like what they say.

124
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,550
OK. I believe you.

125
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:53,860
The adults can solve their own things.

126
00:08:54,590 --> 00:08:55,890
They have nothing to do with us.

127
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:06,360
I don’t think your men can perform opera.

128
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:09,710
You really made a mistake.

129
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,160
Among them,

130
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:14,350
someone sings better than Shang Xirui.

131
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:19,190
OK, don’t beat around the bush.

132
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,320
Come to the point.

133
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:29,970
You’ve taken charge of the chamber for more than 10 years.

134
00:09:31,010 --> 00:09:33,960
You’ve had a lot of enemies and debts.

135
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,560
It’s time to quit.

136
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:44,100
I am the chairman of Peking Chamber of Commerce.

137
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:47,720
Do you think

138
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:49,340
you can make me quit?

139
00:09:51,950 --> 00:09:54,200
You don’t want to leave your wealth?

140
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,970
I’ve been the chairman for 18 years.

141
00:09:57,980 --> 00:10:00,750
I put efforts into it for the half of my life.

142
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:03,150
Why should I quit?

143
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:06,690
For one reason.

144
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,720
Committing murder with bandits.

145
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:12,490
What?

146
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:15,470
The one who did such a vicious thing

147
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:18,300
doesn’t deserve to be the chairman.

148
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:21,630
Nonsense.

149
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:24,030
That’s fictive.

150
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,450
I don’t even know this.

151
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:29,760
Everything needs evidence.

152
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:34,120
I will give you a performance today.

153
00:10:34,570 --> 00:10:36,800
But now you are performing to me.

154
00:10:37,570 --> 00:10:38,520
I said it.

155
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,950
The opera is Returning to Zhao.

156
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:42,590
Watch it.

157
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:48,310
Chaca’er.

158
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:50,640
I’ll finish this book tonight.

159
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,570
I’ll give you back tomorrow.

160
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,700
OK.

161
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,660
See you tomorrow.

162
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,850
My lady, I’ll send Mr. Zheng in.

163
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,390
Please wait me in the car.

164
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:01,330
I’ll be right back.

165
00:11:15,890 --> 00:11:17,910
You must know

166
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:20,390
the first performer.

167
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:23,130
The second chief of Laozi Ridge.

168
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,030
Lower your head.

169
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:36,190
I only know one sentence.

170
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:38,450
The dead can’t be the evidence.

171
00:11:39,340 --> 00:11:40,020
Guards!

172
00:11:48,860 --> 00:11:49,910
Mr. Cheng.

173
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:53,610
You were lucky to escape it.

174
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:57,040
But now you dash into the hell.

175
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:59,510
No one can help you.

176
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,110
None of them can live!

177
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,800
Grandpa! Grandpa!

178
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,970
Help! Grandpa!

179
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:12,260
Grandpa!

180
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,770
Cheng Fengtai, you!

181
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,340
Grandpa! Help!

182
00:12:18,350 --> 00:12:19,720
Everyone is here.

183
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:23,300
-Mr. Zheng, fire a round.
-Help me!

184
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:25,890
Grandpa! Grandpa!

185
00:12:26,130 --> 00:12:27,530
Help!

186
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:29,910
-Save me! Grandpa!
-You!

187
00:12:30,710 --> 00:12:32,190
Help!

188
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,110
Grandpa!

189
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:37,760
Grandpa!

190
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:40,320
-Leave here.
-Help!

191
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:48,920
Cheng Fengtai.

192
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:52,850
He’s still a child.

193
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:54,680
Don’t get him involved.

194
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:56,760
How about this?

195
00:12:58,100 --> 00:12:59,320
I’ll take care

196
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:01,470
of your grandson.

197
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:04,680
As long as you make everything clear,

198
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:09,450
I’ll finish this performance.

199
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:13,090
It’s deal.

200
00:13:15,650 --> 00:13:17,300
I’ll go to police station to confess.

201
00:13:22,490 --> 00:13:23,410
Mr. Zheng!

202
00:13:30,340 --> 00:13:31,590
Well, Mr. Shang.

203
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:33,750
Is this interesting?

204
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:45,330
Quite good.

205
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:49,840
Exciting.

206
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,690
Mr. Cheng.

207
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:54,550
Do you always do business in this way?

208
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:57,280
My business is thrilling.

209
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,050
There are many interesting things.

210
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,590
Will you go with me in the future?

211
00:14:01,810 --> 00:14:02,310
Yes.

212
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,970
I’m waiting on you.

213
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:15,840
Peking Chamber of Commerce is totally messy.

214
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:19,690
It’s not enough to make Zheng quit.

215
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:22,920
The whole industry is disordered.

216
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:26,790
If there’s not a good man being the new chairman,

217
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:30,280
I still can’t sleep well.

218
00:14:31,230 --> 00:14:32,600
He’s not a good man,

219
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,350
but you are.

220
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:36,740
Why don’t you take his place?

221
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,550
Fengtai.

222
00:14:47,650 --> 00:14:50,020
Concubines in the palace used this way.

223
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:50,890
It’s really useful.

224
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:53,240
Take these medicine for several months,

225
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:54,850
and you’ll get good news.

226
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:00,230
That’s great.

227
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:02,420
How can I repay you?

228
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:08,860
Chacha’er, you are back?

229
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:10,510
You don’t you say hi to Mengping?

230
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:15,310
What’s wrong with this kid?

231
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,630
She’s weird.

232
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,000
It’s fine.

233
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,120
Mengping, how are you?

234
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:23,180
Good evening.

235
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:26,270
You made your sister angry?

236
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:27,280
No.

237
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,050
Kids are always childish.

238
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:31,480
Mengping, have a seat at here.

239
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,620
I need to leave.

240
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,450
What’s the matter?

241
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:00,300
Is Chacha’er still in her room?

242
00:16:00,310 --> 00:16:02,460
Miss Cheng locks her door.

243
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:03,970
She didn’t come out even though I called her.

244
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:07,020
After she went back with Fengtai,

245
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,450
she didn’t go out of her room.

246
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,530
Fengtai was worried a whole night.

247
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:12,940
He didn’t sleep well.

248
00:16:12,950 --> 00:16:14,330
This morning,

249
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:16,600
Mr. Cheng wanted to drive Miss Cheng to school.

250
00:16:16,610 --> 00:16:18,010
She stood at her door

251
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,540
for half an hour.

252
00:16:19,670 --> 00:16:21,650
But Miss Cheng didn’t open the door.

253
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:25,150
This girl is more stubborn

254
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,010
than a man.

255
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:28,570
Let me have a try.

256
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:43,810
Chacha’er.

257
00:16:44,590 --> 00:16:45,880
Time for lunch.

258
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:48,500
Girls too thin

259
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,550
don’t look pretty.

260
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:54,620
I know

261
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,040
you quarreled with your brother.

262
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,610
You are good girl.

263
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:01,420
It must be your brother’s fault.

264
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,940
Tell me how he treated you.

265
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:07,480
I’ll ask him to apologize to you, OK?

266
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:14,290
I don’t need his apology.

267
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,119
I want him to tell the police

268
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,089
to release Zheng Laihong’s grandpa.

269
00:17:18,349 --> 00:17:19,869
Zheng Laihong’s grandpa?

270
00:17:21,010 --> 00:17:23,050
You mean Chairman Zheng?

271
00:17:24,950 --> 00:17:27,089
Is this related to your brother?

272
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,150
My brother asked police

273
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,690
to arrest Zheng Laihong’s grandpa.

274
00:17:32,670 --> 00:17:35,070
Maybe he did

275
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,090
something guilty,

276
00:17:36,270 --> 00:17:37,570
so the police arrested him.

277
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:38,930
No.

278
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:41,690
Before you are clear of the whole story,

279
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:43,190
you had a quarrel with him.

280
00:17:44,370 --> 00:17:45,230
Also,

281
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:48,350
this is the adults’ thing on business.

282
00:17:48,690 --> 00:17:50,970
What you need to do is studying and living happily.

283
00:17:50,980 --> 00:17:52,170
Don’t care about this.

284
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,700
I don’t care this.

285
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:57,920
I only know that my brother used me

286
00:17:57,930 --> 00:17:58,960
to cheat Zhong Laihong

287
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:00,410
and threaten his grandpa.

288
00:18:02,090 --> 00:18:04,580
My... My brother is too cunning.

289
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,970
I become a joint criminal now.

290
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:09,080
Welcome.

291
00:18:09,090 --> 00:18:09,900
Congratulations.

292
00:18:09,910 --> 00:18:11,270
