293
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,350
Come in, please.

294
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,700
Come in, please.

295
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:21,900
Mr. Cheng, you are here?

296
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:22,670
Lord An.

297
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:24,970
Today is the madam’s birthday.

298
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:26,320
As her nephew-in-law,

299
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:28,050
I should come to congratulate her.

300
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:31,680
OK.

301
00:18:31,910 --> 00:18:32,870
Thanks.

302
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:36,340
