303
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:37,880
It’s like a real one.

304
00:18:40,940 --> 00:18:42,360
Here’s a pigtail.

305
00:18:42,370 --> 00:18:43,570
It’s complete.

306
00:18:43,580 --> 00:18:44,670
Don’t make fun of me.

307
00:18:45,010 --> 00:18:46,920
This is a fake pigtail.

308
00:18:47,470 --> 00:18:48,760
But this robe

309
00:18:48,770 --> 00:18:49,890
is a real one

310
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,080
that I wore in the palace before.

311
00:18:53,430 --> 00:18:54,200
I also have

312
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:55,710
a robe for prince.

313
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:57,940
But it’s a pity that the emperor left the palace in a hurry,

314
00:18:58,330 --> 00:19:00,260
