315
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:02,350
I won’t wear it today.

316
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,730
The emperor is sneezing in the northeast.

317
00:19:06,770 --> 00:19:08,670
Every time I chat with you,

318
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:11,170
You’ll mention the emperor.

319
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,920
You put a lot of efforts into dressing.

320
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:17,520
But...

321
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:20,280
