322
00:19:20,290 --> 00:19:21,780
This is only the beginning.

323
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:24,800
You’ll be shocked after you go in.

324
00:19:25,490 --> 00:19:27,550
My mom prepared everything

325
00:19:28,010 --> 00:19:30,270
