326
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,260
OK.

327
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:33,140
I have no choice.

328
00:19:33,470 --> 00:19:34,520
She had a disease

329
00:19:34,530 --> 00:19:35,380
