330
00:19:35,630 --> 00:19:36,950
So she’s muddleheaded.

331
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:40,100
She thinks we are in Guangxu’s period.

332
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:42,930
Mr. Cheng, after you go,

333
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,310
