334
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:45,220
OK.

335
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:47,100
Today is her birthday.

336
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:47,650
OK.

337
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:48,810
Thanks, Mr. Cheng.

338
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:49,580
Please go in.

339
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:57,790
Mr. Cheng.

340
00:19:59,520 --> 00:20:01,930
Mr. Cheng.

341
00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:03,630
Mr. Cheng.

342
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:14,450
Mr. Shang.

343
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:18,900
Why are you hiding here?

344
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:21,430
I was waiting for you for long.

345
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:23,450
I came for you specially.

346
00:20:23,810 --> 00:20:24,710
You should be grateful.

347
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:27,290
No one wants to see the fake pigtail.

348
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:30,090
I’m helping you open your horizons.

349
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:32,750
You are the investor of Shuiyun Theater.

350
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:35,250
So you need to see more things

351
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:36,190
