352
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:38,950
OK, I’ll open my horizon.

353
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:40,210
Show me the way.

354
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:50,150
Here. Here.

355
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:53,060
Put the chicken first.

356
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:55,220
And then, the ribs.

357
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:58,400
Stewed pork is next to ribs.

358
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,550
The soup is in front of them.

359
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:06,530
It looks good now.

360
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:08,780
Go out.

361
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:14,430
Nice.

362
00:21:15,970 --> 00:21:17,070
You cooked these dishes.

363
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:17,960
You really put a lot of efforts.

364
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,310
Commander

365
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:21,100
