383
00:22:07,130 --> 00:22:07,640
Yes.

384
00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:08,810
Did you sleep well?

385
00:22:08,820 --> 00:22:09,530
Yes.

386
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,670
Did you miss me?

387
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,810
Yes.

388
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:17,560
