389
00:22:17,970 --> 00:22:19,670
How long haven’t you shaved?

390
00:22:19,910 --> 00:22:21,340
It hurts.

391
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:25,080
Darling, shave for me tonight.

392
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,250
Look at you.

393
00:22:27,870 --> 00:22:29,290
Come on. Come to eat.

394
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:29,730
OK.

395
00:22:29,740 --> 00:22:31,390
I’ll shave for you after lunch.

396
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:33,080
OK, thanks, darling.

397
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:35,950
Drink.

398
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:36,690
OK.

399
00:22:40,510 --> 00:22:41,120
Wait.

400
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,170
I’m waiting for you.

401
00:22:44,970 --> 00:22:46,390
Toast you.

402
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:46,800
OK.

403
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:47,910
Welcome home.

404
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,710
OK.

405
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:56,630
Here.

406
00:22:58,260 --> 00:23:00,520
Have a tofu with crab.

407
00:23:01,570 --> 00:23:02,190
Do you like it?

408
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:07,240
You cooked it?

409
00:23:07,250 --> 00:23:08,230
Of Course.

410
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:10,950
You are better than those cooks.

411
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,410
Have more if you like.

412
00:23:14,420 --> 00:23:14,940
OK.

413
00:23:14,950 --> 00:23:15,880
I’ll

414
00:23:15,890 --> 00:23:17,890
go with you wherever you go,

415
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:19,590
and I can cook this for you every day.

416
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:21,670
When I was alone in Peking...

417
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:25,320
Forget it. You are just back.

418
00:23:25,330 --> 00:23:26,690
I won’t mention these annoying things.

419
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:28,470
What happened?

420
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:31,220
Did your brother make you angry again?

421
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,190
How dare he?

422
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:36,470
I just think

423
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:39,370
it’s not easy to be a step-mother.

424
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,650
It’s the prat Cao Guixiu

425
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:45,910
