430
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:03,400
I can’t bear it.

431
00:24:04,010 --> 00:24:04,930
He said...

432
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:30,460
This theater is really splendid.

433
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,110
Look at the painting and the sculpture.

434
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:33,950
Huibin and Yahong

435
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:35,020
