438
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:42,820
It’s really delicate.

439
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:45,290
An Mansion must invest a lot.

440
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:46,800
You don’t know it.

441
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:49,340
This theater was built

442
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:51,750
