443
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:54,260
Three emperors watched opera here.

444
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,150
Can it be botchy?

445
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:14,140
♬ Time to go ♬

446
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:27,460
Shunzi. Shunzi.

447
00:25:27,730 --> 00:25:28,740
Why did you run here?

448
00:25:32,450 --> 00:25:34,340
Shunzi. Shunzi.

449
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:37,860
Shunzi. Go.

450
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,720
Let’s go to congratulate the madam.

451
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:42,240
Mr. Cheng.

452
00:25:43,600 --> 00:25:44,140
What do you think of it?

453
00:25:46,990 --> 00:25:47,970
It’s delicate.

454
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:49,370
And the sound effect is good.

455
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,370
Even the dog was appealed.

456
00:25:57,470 --> 00:26:00,530
I didn’t think I can sing at here.

457
00:26:01,860 --> 00:26:03,550
You like here so much?

458
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:05,550
Of course.

459
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:08,740
If only our theater

460
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:10,940
