461
00:26:12,140 --> 00:26:13,740
You are not a picky one.

462
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:16,430
I’ll imitate here and build a theater.

463
00:26:17,150 --> 00:26:20,070
The fake is fake.

464
00:26:20,670 --> 00:26:23,200
It can’t be imitated.

465
00:26:23,470 --> 00:26:24,420
Mr. Cheng. Come with me.

466
00:26:25,470 --> 00:26:26,070
What?

467
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:28,210
Sit at the emperor’s chair!

468
00:26:46,380 --> 00:26:49,970
The emperor must sit here.

469
00:26:52,210 --> 00:26:53,430
Mr. Cheng. Come.

470
00:26:58,050 --> 00:26:58,640
Forget it.

471
00:26:59,490 --> 00:27:01,100
You won’t understand.

472
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:02,980
Don’t waste time.

473
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:06,540
That’s enough, Mr. Shang.

474
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,790
You need to prepare.

475
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,680
Go to have a chat with them.

476
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:11,590
Leave me alone.

477
00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:13,490
Let me enjoy this feeling for a while.

478
00:27:24,290 --> 00:27:26,550
