479
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,870
Who are you?

480
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:45,240
Why should he inform you?

481
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:51,220
I am the doctor of the commander.

482
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:52,550
Nice to meet you.

483
00:28:01,910 --> 00:28:04,260
This is made by crab roe.

484
00:28:05,050 --> 00:28:06,320
You have coronary heart disease.

485
00:28:06,990 --> 00:28:09,620
You can’t eat food with high cholesterol.

486
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:14,710
Look at me.

487
00:28:17,560 --> 00:28:19,460
When did you get coronary heart disease?

488
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:21,670
I don’t even know.

489
00:28:24,230 --> 00:28:26,740
Several days ago,

490
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:28,390
