491
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:31,460
I almost couldn’t get up.

492
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:36,000
Why didn’t you tell me such a big thing?

493
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:37,060
No...

494
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:37,880
I...

495
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:39,390
I have medicine

496
00:28:39,820 --> 00:28:40,770
and a doctor.

497
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,030
So I didn’t tell you

498
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:43,360
in case you worry.

499
00:28:43,630 --> 00:28:45,180
You should tell me at least.

500
00:28:45,630 --> 00:28:47,470
It’s convenient to call me from your barrack.

501
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:50,660
Call me once a day in future.

502
00:28:51,060 --> 00:28:52,090
OK. OK.

503
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,690
Don’t eat tofu.

504
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:55,430
Here.

505
00:28:56,030 --> 00:28:56,910
Have a rib.

506
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:57,710
OK.

507
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:59,290
Pork with fat

508
00:28:59,460 --> 00:29:00,810
