509
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:04,260
Commander has a sign of having diabetes.

510
00:29:04,800 --> 00:29:07,360
He can’t eat this

511
00:29:07,370 --> 00:29:08,770
no matter from the material

512
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:10,750
or the way to cook.

513
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:13,980
Commander,

514
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:17,630
