515
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:25,980
What do you mean?

516
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:28,550
Yours is nutritive.

517
00:29:28,910 --> 00:29:31,260
Commander’s favorite dishes made by me

518
00:29:31,430 --> 00:29:32,460
