519
00:29:34,380 --> 00:29:36,790
I care commander’s health more than anyone else.

520
00:29:37,070 --> 00:29:39,190
I don’t think I need to ask you

521
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:41,440
what he can eat.

522
00:29:42,120 --> 00:29:43,470
You are commander’s wife.

523
00:29:44,010 --> 00:29:46,340
Absolutely, you care him most.

524
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:48,540
But as long as you

525
00:29:48,550 --> 00:29:50,710
know something about nutriology,

526
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:53,460
I can go now.

527
00:29:54,770 --> 00:29:55,910
Who is she?

528
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:58,100
She’s here to argue with me.

529
00:29:58,320 --> 00:29:59,840
Say something.

530
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:01,610
Darling.

531
00:30:02,660 --> 00:30:04,030
She’s a doctor.

532
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:05,850
All doctors treat the patient

533
00:30:05,860 --> 00:30:07,120
