537
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:15,460
I have...

538
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:16,980
I have some diseases.

539
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:18,590
They were found already.

540
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:21,430
I may fall down one day.

541
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:22,670
Didn’t you see that

542
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:25,030
I gave my military power

543
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:28,040
to Cao Guixiu?

544
00:30:28,810 --> 00:30:29,640
Really?

545
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,050
So...

546
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:34,370
You...

547
00:30:34,820 --> 00:30:37,270
You really have these diseases that she said?

548
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:37,990
Yes.

549
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,620
Why...

550
00:30:39,630 --> 00:30:41,260
Why didn’t you tell me?

551
00:30:42,940 --> 00:30:43,460
Why...

552
00:30:43,470 --> 00:30:45,190
Why didn’t you tell me?

553
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:48,870
You are still young.

554
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,690
If I’m healthy,

555
00:30:51,090 --> 00:30:52,380
I can stay with you longer.

556
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:53,710
Doctor Kimura

557
00:30:53,940 --> 00:30:57,040
studied in Japanese Medical University.

558
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,790
What we eat and use

559
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:03,110
