560
00:31:03,290 --> 00:31:05,190
It won’t be wrong to listen to her.

561
00:31:06,930 --> 00:31:07,710
Change the dishes.

562
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,590
Eat her nutritive lunch.

563
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:20,820
I won’t bother you here.

564
00:31:49,330 --> 00:31:50,110
Sirs.

565
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:51,910
Did you see Mr. Shang?

566
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,840
-No.
-No.

567
00:31:56,090 --> 00:31:58,190
Sirs, did you see Mr. Shang?

568
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,290
-No.
-No.

569
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:03,670
Sirs.

570
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:04,820
What are you looking for?

571
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,660
Did you see Mr. Shang?

572
00:32:07,420 --> 00:32:08,210
Mr. Shang?

573
00:32:08,220 --> 00:32:09,130
Is he missing again?

574
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:09,860
Yes.

575
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:11,530
The performance will begin in half an hour.

576
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:13,260
I didn’t see him at the back stage.

577
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,570
So I came here to find him.

578
00:32:14,580 --> 00:32:15,710
We didn’t see him

579
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:16,790
